ERIE RAILROAD COMPANY, Appellant, v. Horace MIZELL, as Receiver of the Citizens National Bank & Trust Company of Hornell, New York, Respondent. No. 73. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. Nov. 30, 1936. John W. Hollis, of Hornell, N. Y., for appellant. Harry L. Allen, of Hornell, N. Y. (Harold G. Hutchens, of Rocliester, N. Y., of counsel), for respondent.

Before L. HAND, SWAN, and CHASE, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Judgment (9 F.Supp. 143) affirmed.
